-- QUOTE BOX: GM and Chrysler hold merger talks
-- 
-- Mon Oct 13, 2008 10:53am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/13/us-gm-quote-box-idUSTRE49C53220081013

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - General Motors has had talks with smaller rival Chrysler LLC about a merger that would combine the No. 1 and No. 3 American automakers at a time when both are struggling to cut costs and shore up cash, according to a source briefed on the matter. 

 The following are comments from analysts and industry insiders on the potential tie-up between the two large auto makers.